<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbd7d3f87-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c" identifier="/us/usc/t31/s6106"><num value="6106">§ 6106.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">After <date date="1983-10-01">October 1, 1983</date>, there may be appropriated to the Administrator such sums as may be necessary to carry out the responsibilities of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbd7d3f88-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/98/169/s5">Pub. L. 98–169, § 5</ref>, <date date="1983-11-29">Nov. 29, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/1115">97 Stat. 1115</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
